-He wants to carry
a cup of coffee

00:06:59.140 --> 00:07:03.380
around without burning himself,
and that's very, very different

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:06.167
from other people, other
clients, had in mind.

00:07:06.167 --> 00:07:07.625
But this project's
very mechanical.

00:07:07.625 --> 00:07:10.476
It' very simple, yet a
really challenging problem.

