we've been trying out a
lot of different prototypes

00:08:33.165 --> 00:08:38.390
with Paul, mainly things
that we found online,

00:08:38.390 --> 00:08:43.630
some things like this on-stage
cup holder, which is basically

00:08:43.630 --> 00:08:46.850
a cup holder that can
statically be just clicked

00:08:46.850 --> 00:08:53.770
on to his crutch, and it
