wanted as little material

01:29:38.000 --> 01:29:40.580
on her hand as possible, so it
wouldn't weigh her down and so

01:29:40.580 --> 01:29:42.800
that it wouldn't look like
a very obvious device.

01:29:42.800 --> 01:29:44.180
And then on the
