02:21:37.870 --> 02:21:39.640
work through our
software prototype,

02:21:39.640 --> 02:21:42.760
and by the end of that, have
something to present to Chris

02:21:42.760 --> 02:21:44.750
and have him actually
test it and use it

02:21:44.750 --> 02:21:46.432
so that way we can
revise and reiterate

02:21:46.432 --> 02:21:47.390
and keep going with it.

02:21:47.390 --> 02:21:49.150
And by the end of
November, we want

02:21:49.150 --> 02:21:52.150
to have our final version
that we can continue

02:21:52.150 --> 02:21:53.633
to reiterate throughout.

