02:43:31.300 --> 02:43:34.510
his left arm, and
this has also resulted

02:43:34.510 --> 02:43:37.010
in cognitive
difficulties, especially

02:43:37.010 --> 02:43:39.336
in the late afternoon
or early afternoon,

02:43:39.336 --> 02:43:41.460
whenever sometimes it's a
little bit harder for him

02:43:41.460 --> 02:43:45.340
to process and to focus
and to just kind of stay

02:43:45.340 --> 02:43:47.390
on track with
whatever conversation

02:43:47.390 --> 02:43:48.700
he's currently engaged in.

