He was very, very opposed
to having something

02:48:39.040 --> 02:48:42.910
big and clunky in his
desk or his workspace

02:48:42.910 --> 02:48:43.910
whenever he was cooking.

02:48:43.910 --> 02:48:47.464
And we used that to
further our designs

02:48:47.464 --> 02:48:49.880
and make sure that we go with
something smaller, something

02:48:49.880 --> 02:48:54.190
that doesn't get in the way and
is very easy for him to use.

